{"tid":767403,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「KIKI挑戰」狂人出現　530萬人看他噴屎","createTime":"2018-08-04T12:58:11.000Z","updateTime":"2018-08-06T10:46:38.000Z","uid":61543,"like":1,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":7,"replies":[{"pid":"828e2bf82a22502f67c1af2a831ca0ae43b54447","tid":767403,"uid":61543,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T12:58:11.000Z","msg":"近來全球瘋玩行進間開車門在路邊跳舞的「KIKI挑戰」(Kiki Challenge)，有位網友「MacSavage」堪稱是最狂KIKI挑戰者，他跳舞跳到一半開始拉屎，而且沒有擦屁股就坐回車上。<br />\n「KIKI挑戰」使用的歌曲為加拿大饒舌歌手Drake的《Inmyfeelings》，這一波風潮從知名網紅Shiggy開始，他在Instagram上分享自己跟著這首歌跳舞的影片後引起許多人跟跟風挑戰。不過由於有人挑戰時發生車禍等事故，所以有些國家的警方呼籲民眾別進行「KIKI挑戰」。<br />\n而有位網友「MacSavage」，日前在《臉書》分享他的「KIKI挑戰」影片，不到一個禮拜的時間就吸引了530萬次觀看，他與一般挑戰者相同，都是在行進間下車在路邊跳舞，但是他跳到一半後拉下褲子半蹲噴屎，噴完後再迅速坐回車內。<br />\n這段超狂挑戰影片，讓網友紛紛留言「他竟然沒有擦就坐回去了.....」、「這應該是至今最狂的挑戰者」、「如果是我的話，我才不會讓他坐回車內」、「為什麼可以這麼順暢的噴出來」、「看了以後覺得超噁心」。（即時新聞中心／綜合報導）<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180804/1404685\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180804%2F1404685&d=RZ8hy5wQ06NL2BZ5%2FpVUWTCdMQr7etzq9tFbjrA%2B72k%3D&h=944d075f\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Ftw.appledaily.com%2Finternational%2Frealtime%2F20180804%2F1404685&h=79205270\" target=\"_blank\">https://tw.appledaily.com/international/realtime/20180804/1404685</a>"},{"pid":"b225fe39eb7cd9c1794ce06590e678ed66444160","tid":767403,"uid":40903,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-04T13:36:50.000Z","msg":"wtf <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"52d3a6ce3c23852fca0e2e024b6202c0ad8e82bf","tid":767403,"uid":166675,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-08-05T12:12:24.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/haha.gif\" class=\"hkgmoj